Reasoning: The paper deals with soft decision fusion in a wireless sensor network, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI). The problem of detecting an intruder over a fading channel also involves control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.MA). The use of quantization in the fusion rules also involves multimedia (cs.MM).
